    <item>
      <title>华尔街不断扩大的贸易压力指数追踪数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/wall-street-s-broadening-trade-imperils-index-tracking-billions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期以来梦寐以求的股市大涨势头的扩大对大量积极管理者和宏观多头来说是个好消息。然而，对于那些年复一年在指数跟踪工具上投入数十亿美元的投资者来说，这预示着一路上的痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/wall-street-s-broadening-trade-imperils-index-tracking-billions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 20:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
